ations \/\/ For some utilities"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Or more simple, import umbrella library","type":"heading","anchor":"Or-more-simple-import-umbrella-library","level":3},{"name":"Note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We do not recommend this solution because from our point of view use of tailored imports is better to import only the needed elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use of umbrella products can increase app sizes and needed storage because it emebds plenty of assets (images, fonts, etc.)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and useless constants."}]}],"type":"aside","style":"note"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Import the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}]},{"type":"text","text":" product which suits your needs:"}]},{"type":"table","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Umbrella"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUI"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above and all themes","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrange"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Orange Compact themes"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIWireframe"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above but with only Wireframe theme"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrangeSosh"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Sosh themes"}]}]]],"header":"row"},{"text":"Chose your theme","type":"heading","anchor"